title: Cave Reflection
description: A close-up view of a rocky cave wall with vibrant colors, reflecting in clear blue water. The rocks display shades of orange, yellow, and brown, while the water is a bright turquoise, creating a serene and picturesque scene.

title: Aerial View of a Glacier
description: An aerial view of a large glacier flowing through a mountainous landscape. The glacier is predominantly white and blue, with visible crevasses and ridges. Surrounding the glacier are rugged mountains, some capped with snow, and green hillsides, indicating a diverse terrain. The sky is clear with a few clouds, suggesting a bright and sunny day.

title: Geometric Shape
description: A 3D geometric shape that appears to be a rectangular prism with a curved top. The upper part is a light blue color, while the lower part is a darker blue, creating a gradient effect. The shape has a smooth surface and a flat base.

title: 3D Cylinder with a Cut
description: A 3D representation of a transparent cylinder with a vertical cut. The cylinder has a smooth surface and a flat top, with a rectangular section removed from the side, revealing the interior.

title: Aerial View of a River in a Dense Forest
description: An aerial view showcasing a winding river flowing through a lush, green forest. The landscape is dominated by dense foliage, with various shades of green, and the river appears to be a vibrant blue, contrasting beautifully with the surrounding vegetation.

title: Scenic Mountain Lake
description: A picturesque landscape featuring a serene lake surrounded by lush green meadows and rolling hills. In the background, a prominent mountain rises, partially covered with rocky outcrops. The sky is bright with fluffy white clouds, creating a vibrant and tranquil atmosphere.
